{"tid":1175643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最賺錢YouTuber 7歲瑞安去年賺1.7億","createTime":"2019-05-28T16:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T11:53:01.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e0a6d8eb45aa67581e17f4d32eebda3bfa14fa","tid":1175643,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"最賺錢YouTuber 7歲瑞安去年賺1.7億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190526/s00064/61d7235d9b29ec73593f46f2072142d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190526%2Fs00064%2F61d7235d9b29ec73593f46f2072142d4.jpg&h=a8aa5024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《福布斯》去年底公布的數據，2018年賺錢最多的YouTube網紅，是YouTube頻道「瑞安玩具評測」（Ryan ToysReview）的主持人&mdash;&mdash;年約7歲的瑞安（Ryan）。他在2017年6月1日至18年6月1日期間，賺進了2200萬美元（約1.7億港元）的稅前收入，較前一年同期高出1倍。2017年他在該網紅收入榜排名第8。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安本身很喜歡看玩具評測影片，希望像其他小朋友一樣在YouTube介紹玩具。自2015年3月，年約4歲的瑞安開始拍片上載YouTube，試玩各式玩具。他認為自己大受歡迎，是因為他有趣又有娛樂性。 他的頻道目前有超過1900萬訂戶，瀏覽次數超過292億次。經瑞安介紹過的玩具，往往大受歡迎。在合作伙伴Pocket.watch的協助下，瑞安已簽署40項全球許可協議，生產睡衣、配飾、萬聖節服裝、派對用品、家具及家居用品等。<br />\n<br />\nYouTube有多個給博主賺錢的方式，例如透過合作伙伴計劃（YouTube Partner Program, YPP），讓上載者可透過自己的影片賺取廣告收入。YouTube的廣告播放平台Adsense會在影片中自動安插廣告，如果廣告累積到一定數量的觀眾收看，就可獲取廣告分紅。<br />\n<br />\n千次點擊可分1美元廣告利潤<br />\n一般來說，平均1000次點擊，約可分得1美元的廣告利潤。但上載者必須先滿足一些條件，才有資格申請加入YPP計劃。條件包括：頻道的訂戶必須至少有1000人。在過去12個月，頻道累計觀看總時數要超越4000小時。換言之，即平均每日頻道的觀看時間要接近11小時，對網絡新人的門檻相當高。目前遊戲界的網紅大受歡迎，他們利用遊戲直播，分享自己的打機心得和經驗，吸引很多玩家收看。也有網紅透過YouTube直播功能，在網上拍賣物品賺錢。"},{"pid":"2a95df5082e85db1cd314ae90318d96d2449aef0","tid":1175643,"uid":247836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2342689ea34b3c8138461de82320e0a71ba13da3","tid":1175643,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"教煮餸大叔應該要狙擊呢條細路"},{"pid":"937142cc6fc217390bb046af4cb88c099b83fa1e","tid":1175643,"uid":203251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c64f90cd9ab29e256da634ae8a61604be108beb","tid":1175643,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得我的人生已經走到盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d764195b81c4d8a6b04b32a2485c4f7ca66d6bed","tid":1175643,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd21d4333b5600d5a737726c682e002b68256244","tid":1175643,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c1fa6282ed8e0378f41c23ac6f298ab66fa7f9","tid":1175643,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"賴仁"},{"pid":"ff6ea73e8a10f1782602d839659e88b6c8ff3ed5","tid":1175643,"uid":46896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"我以為起樓果間瑞安賺1.7億, 睇怕我要去驗眼"},{"pid":"15d92b296bd4d00fa42960f4f5e0150d5552e116","tid":1175643,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"強烈讉責唔讀書走去做YOUTUBER<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9b7381750ce5e9cd61fd2e56710c58ffea0b7a","tid":1175643,"uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56de93dd6bcdc1e4fa2756fa83eab817460f3ea4","